sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Utente
    participant T as Telegram API
    participant n8n
    participant E as Email (Gmail / Outlook)
    participant AI as AI (Basic LLM Chain)

    %% Workflow 3 (Gmail) / Workflow 4 (Outlook)

    E->>n8n: Email Trigger: nuova email non letta

    par Classificazione e lista label/cartelle in parallelo
        n8n->>AI: Basic LLM Chain: oggetto + anteprima
        AI-->>n8n: categoria (es. "n8n/newsletter")
    and
        n8n->>E: Get Many Labels (Gmail) / Get Many Folders (Outlook)
        E-->>n8n: lista label/cartelle con ID
    end

    n8n->>n8n: Merge: combina categoria + lista
    n8n->>n8n: Code: trova label/folder ID per nome

    alt Gmail
        n8n->>E: Gmail: Add Label (label ID)
    else Outlook
        n8n->>E: Outlook: Move Message (folder ID)
    end

    alt Email urgente
        n8n->>T: Telegram: notifica email urgente (Chat ID fisso)
        T-->>U: 🚨 Email urgente da: ...
    end
